    "description": "单枪匹马，或者和最多4名朋友一起探索诡异的鬼屋和废墟，搜索神秘的“怨念的象征”。<br><br>怨念会化作恶灵大肆破坏，千万不能放松警惕。启动紫外线，在黑暗中击退怨灵，保持理智，争取时间！<br><br>将“怨念的象征”全部放到魔法阵上，即可净化恶灵。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多平台操作：</h2>除标准键鼠之外，《Paranormal Hunter》还可以使用VR设备Oculus Rift，以及支持Xinput的操纵器和手柄进行游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人在线合作：</h2>和最多4名玩家合作游戏，在恶灵袭来之前找到“怨念的象征”！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机变化：</h2>关卡动态生成，带来绝不重复的未知恐怖体验。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> &quot;怨念的象征&quot; 不一定会出现在相同地点。<br></li><li>阻挡去路的瓦砾不一定每次都会堵在相同地点。<br></li><li>魔法阵不一定总是出现在相同地点。。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >循环游戏：</h2>驱逐恶灵获得报酬，即可购买有助于今后游戏的道具。但请注意，如果未能生还，携入道具就会全部丢失。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种道具：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>幽灵探测器</li></ul>可以探测幽灵的气息。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/9d6c61afdcd046edc8759488c66dcc39.poster.avif?t=1684805406\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/9d6c61afdcd046edc8759488c66dcc39.webm?t=1684805406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/9d6c61afdcd046edc8759488c66dcc39.mp4?t=1684805406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>线香</li></ul>散发着恶灵厌恶的香气。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/04d707b224496ab9bb312d935dc4954d.poster.avif?t=1684805406\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/04d707b224496ab9bb312d935dc4954d.webm?t=1684805406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/04d707b224496ab9bb312d935dc4954d.mp4?t=1684805406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>护身符</li></ul>可以在恶灵眼前隐身。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/5d18f23d26308dc9458ab39eab083451.poster.avif?t=1684805406\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/5d18f23d26308dc9458ab39eab083451.webm?t=1684805406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777600/extras/5d18f23d26308dc9458ab39eab083451.mp4?t=1684805406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
